 《AV Splat》事件一年后，参与者之一VTuber再次发声https://p2y.jp/1-year-after-av-splatoon-problem-one-of-the-participants-vtuber-ikinone-tomeru-has-speaking-again/ https://p2y.jp/1-year-after-av-splatoon-problem-one-of-the-participants-vtuber-ikinone-tomeru-has-speaking-again/#respondp2y_admin Sat, 28 Oct 2023 11:18:41 +0000 VTuberゲームバーチャル任天堂AVスプラTwitchYouTubeYouTuberけんきバーチャルYouTuberプロゲーマー息根とめる深層組 https://p2y.jp/?p=104642 <p> 2023年10月27日（令和5年），VTuber Sone Tomeru（所属：新城组）与职业游戏玩家Kenki一起参加了关于成为问题的所谓“AV Splat”的广播。问题 […]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/1-year-after-av-splatoon-problem-one-of-the-participants-vtuber-ikinone-tomeru-has-speaking-again/">“AV Splat”事件一年后，参与者之一 VTuber 再次发声的帖子</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> 2023年10月27日（令和5年），VTuber <strong>Sone Tomeru</strong> （属于Shinzo-gumi）与职业游戏玩家<strong>Kenki</strong>一起参加了关于成为问题的所谓“ <strong>AV Splat</strong> ”的广播，并就该问题发表了声明。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="73722" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/splatoon-3-collaboration-streaming-av-splatoon-by-vtuber-is-controversial-possible-violation-of-nintendo-and-youtube-terms-and-conditions/splatoon_3_collaboration_streaming_adult_video_splatoon_by_vtuber_and_others_is_controversial_possible_violation_of_nintendo_and_youtube_terms_and_conditions/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/splatoon_3_collaboration_streaming_adult_video_splatoon_by_vtuber_and_others_is_controversial_possible_violation_of_nintendo_and_youtube_terms_and_conditions.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="splatoon_3_collaboration_streaming_adult_video_splatoon_by_vtuber_is_controversial_possible_violation_of_nintendo_and_youtube_terms_and_conditions" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/splatoon_3_collaboration_streaming_adult_video_splatoon_by_vtuber_and_others_is_controversial_possible_violation_of_nintendo_and_youtube_terms_and_conditions.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/splatoon_3_collaboration_streaming_adult_video_splatoon_by_vtuber_and_others_is_controversial_possible_violation_of_nintendo_and_youtube_terms_and_conditions.jpg" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/splatoon_3_collaboration_streaming_adult_video_splatoon_by_vtuber_and_others_is_controversial_possible_violation_of_nintendo_and_youtube_terms_and_conditions.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-73722"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> © 深海集团</figcaption></figure><p>什么是“AV Splat”？2022年（令和4）10月8日21:00，VTuber Kimiko Kikaze（独立），Shigure（同上），Hinachun（隶属：Sensity Club/成人视频女演员）由多个人进行发行比如任天堂的游戏软件《Splatoon 3》的《Splatoon 3》游戏模式《Nawabari Battle》，<strong>背景是透明的，背景是透明的，是关于流视频的</strong>。这极有可能是违反了任天堂和YouTube的条款和条件，并在发布后发展成所谓的“火焰”情况。除了参与者纷纷发表道歉之外，Tomeru Sone等数人的YouTube频道也被暂停，他们实际上被禁止进入YouTube。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="AxThqMxASm"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/av-splatoon-articles-list-participant-ikinone-tomeru-organizer-kikaze-kimiko-and-correspondence-of-nintendo-and-youtube/">【不定期更新】AV Splat参与者屏住呼吸、组织者Kimiko Kikaze、任天堂/YouTube回应等文章列表</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“[不时更新]文章列表，包括 AV Splatoon 参与者、组织者 Kimiko Kikaze、任天堂和 YouTube 的回应等” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/av-splatoon-articles-list-participant-ikinone-tomeru-organizer-kikaze-kimiko-and-correspondence-of-nintendo-and-youtube/embed/#?secret=06hZIoT9Ni#?secret=AxThqMxASm" data-secret="AxThqMxASm" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>这次，在与 Kenki 的广播中，曾根 Tomeru 多次发表了有关《AV Splatoon》的言论。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="AV Splatoon VTuber的例子真实到让人发笑[Kenki剪辑]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/u2q4LTJgLOg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="mgunn653f6676190ce" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
