</style><p></p><p>关于在“AV Splat”上播放成人视频的许可，Tomeru Sone 表示<em>，“我必须获得网站运营者的许可才能播放 AV</em> 。”对于这个“管理层”，有可能就是曾根登梅所属的深层组织。</p><p>此外，他目前还在公司内部发表了“<em>我因为自己的行为而漂浮”、“</em><em>我就像那个名字不能被提及的人”、“</em><em>我”等</em>言论。<em>我没有参与任何事情</em>（<em>更不用说合作了</em>）。”Masu。</p><p>有关此发行版的完整内容，请查看下面的 Kenki 发行版存档。 </p><p></p><iframe loading="lazy" src="https://player.twitch.tv/?video=1961327979&#038;parent=P2y.jp" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true" scrolling="no" height="378" width="620"></iframe><p></p><div class="kaerebalink-box" style="text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;font-size:small;zoom: 1;overflow: hidden;"><div class="kaerebalink-image" style="float:left;margin:0 15px 10px 0;"> <a href="https://hb.afl.rakuten.co.jp/hgc/g0000011.9q7wk3f2.g0000011.9q7wl0d7/kaereba_main_202310282015276446?pc=https%3A%2F%2Fproduct.rakuten.co.jp%2Fproduct%2F-%2F8f3f2f24ff5b9ab643c6afbbe9f28323%2F&#038;m=http%3A%2F%2Fm.product.rakuten.co.jp%2Fproduct%2F8f3f2f24ff5b9ab643c6afbbe9f28323%2F" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://thumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp/ran/img/1001/0004/902/370/550/337/10010004902370550337_1.jpg?_ex=320x320" style="border: none;" /></a> </div><div class="kaerebalink-info" style="line-height:120%;zoom: 1;overflow: hidden;"><div class="kaerebalink-name" style="margin-bottom:10px;line-height:120%"> <a href="https://hb.afl.rakuten.co.jp/hgc/g0000011.9q7wk3f2.g0000011.9q7wl0d7/kaereba_main_202310282015276446?pc=https%3A%2F%2Fproduct.rakuten.co.jp%2Fproduct%2F-%2F8f3f2f24ff5b9ab643c6afbbe9f28323%2F&#038;m=http%3A%2F%2Fm.product.rakuten.co.jp%2Fproduct%2F8f3f2f24ff5b9ab643c6afbbe9f28323%2F" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Splatoon 3/Switch/HACPAV5JA/A 适合所有年龄段</a><div class="kaerebalink-powered-date" style="font-size:8pt;margin-top:5px;font-family:verdana;line-height:120%">发布与<a href="https://kaereba.com" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">Kaereba</a> </div></div><div class="kaerebalink-detail" style="margin-bottom:5px;"></div><div class="kaerebalink-link1" sty